# Dialogue Den interface


<li>You will be discussing the solution to a reasoning task.</li>
<li>Please read the task description carefully.</li>
<li>First you will complete the task by yourself. When you are happy with your choice - press the Submit
    button.
</li>
<li>Once every participant completes the task by themselves, you will have to discuss your solutions in the
    chat and possibly revise your selection. Note, that although many groups reach a unanimous decision, you can submit a different solution.
</li>
<li>We have a timer set for 7 minutes, but you can take more time if needed.</li>
<li>You can leave the experiment at any time by pressing the "Leave room" button on the bottom left.</li>
<li>If you are inactive for a prolonged period of time, you will be excluded from the chat room.</li>
<li>You are expected to give your best effort at solving the task. Discuss possible solutions with the other participants.</li>